query: SELECT t.id, a.temperature, a.pressure, a.humidity, an.height, an.weight, f.vo2MaxMlKgMin FROM vo2_max_tests t LEFT JOIN vo2_max_ambient_data a ON t.id = a.testId LEFT JOIN vo2_max_anthropometric an ON t.id = an.testId LEFT JOIN vo2_max_fitness_assessment f ON t.id = f.testId ORDER BY t.uploadedAt DESC LIMIT 1;
